text: Eunidia thomensis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1970.BioLib.cz - Eunidia thomensis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. It occurs in the island of São Tomé.Tavakilian G. & Chevillotte H. (2018). Base de données Titan sur les Cerambycidés ou Longicornes. Eunidia thomensis.
